## Customization Guide\
\
**Before running, customize:**\
- [ ] Roles (lines 8-10)\
- [ ] Locations (lines 12-13)\
- [ ] Current week date (line 41, 45, 49)\
- [ ] Last week date for comparison (line 33)\
- [ ] Attach resume file\
\
**Quick checklist:**\
```\
Today's date: 2026-02-09\
Current week folder: Week_of_2026-02-09\
Last week folder: Week_of_2026-02-02\
Roles: Chief of Staff, Partnerships, [Business Development]\
Locations: [Buenos Aires, Argentina], [Mexico City, Mexico]\
Resume attached: \uc0\u10003 \
```\
\
