\
## Post-Run Actions\
\
After search completes:\
1. Review Current_Top10 file for immediate action items\
2. Update job application tracker (if maintained)\
3. At end of week: Consolidate all searches into Week_[DATE]_MasterList.csv\
\
---\
\
## Performance Notes\
\
**Typical results:**\
- 40-80 jobs extracted\
- 10-20 jobs scoring 70+\
- 5-15 genuinely new jobs (after deduplication + comparison)\
\
**Common issues:**\
- Salary data often missing (50-70% of jobs)\
- Funding status requires extra time if requested\
- Some boards rate-limit after ~20 results per search\
\
**Optimization tips:**\
- Run Sunday mornings (fresh weekly postings)\
- Focus on 2-3 high-priority role types\
- Consider bi-weekly runs instead of daily for broader searches\
\
